        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/37717",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=dasprid",
                        "name": "dasprid",
                        "displayName": "Ben Scholzen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Which PHP Version are you using? There is a known bug with PHP 5.2.0, which was fixed until 5.2.6 or such.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=dasprid",
                        "name": "dasprid",
                        "displayName": "Ben Scholzen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-01-15T06:01:10.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-01-15T06:01:10.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/37720",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=richardnoya",
                        "name": "richardnoya",
                        "displayName": "Richard Noya",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I user PHP 5.3.0",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=richardnoya",
                        "name": "richardnoya",
                        "displayName": "Richard Noya",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-01-15T06:29:19.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-01-15T06:29:19.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/37721",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "My suspicion is that the character is a Latin-1 character.\r\n\r\nWhat happens if you set your view's encoding to 'ISO-8859-1'? You can do this via the view object itself:\r\n{code}\r\n$view->setEncoding('ISO-8859-1');\r\n\/\/ or, in a view script:\r\n$this->setEncoding('ISO-8859-1');\r\n{code}\r\nor, if you're using Zend_Application, via your configuration:\r\n{code}\r\nresources.view.encoding = \"ISO-8859-1\"\r\n{code}\r\nPlease try this and report the results.\r\n\r\nIf that works, then your solution is to do one of the above. If not, we need to investigate further.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-01-15T06:49:44.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-01-15T06:49:44.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/37723",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=richardnoya",
                        "name": "richardnoya",
                        "displayName": "Richard Noya",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I use Zend_Application.\r\nI already had the view encoding on ISO-8859-1\r\n\r\nBut for other reasons I can't recall right now I also implemented this line:\r\n\r\nphpSettings.default_charset = \"ISO-8859-1\"\r\n\r\nRegards Richard.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=richardnoya",
                        "name": "richardnoya",
                        "displayName": "Richard Noya",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-01-15T07:05:11.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-01-15T07:05:11.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/37730",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=richardnoya",
                        "name": "richardnoya",
                        "displayName": "Richard Noya",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Sorry, looked wrong, your suggestion indeed works!\r\nPutting the line resources.view.encoding = \"ISO-8859-1\" in the config file, solved the problem!!\r\n\r\nCan you please explain, why this has to be done only in 1.9.7?\r\n\r\nRgds Richard.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=richardnoya",
                        "name": "richardnoya",
                        "displayName": "Richard Noya",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-01-15T08:44:56.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-01-15T08:44:56.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/37731",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Yes: we changed the default encoding to UTF-8 due to security implications. You can read more about it in the [related security advisory:http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/security\/advisory\/ZF2010-01], which also details the suggestions I made to you in my previous comment.\r\n\r\n(This information was also included in the README.txt in the distribution.)",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-01-15T09:45:04.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-01-15T09:46:04.000+0000"
                }
            ]
        }
    },
